HEADWORD: Lablab
<hw>Lab"lab</hw> <pr>(l⟦acr⟧b"l⟦acr⟧b)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>
<fld>(Bot.)</fld> <def>an East Indian name for several twining
leguminous plants related to the bean, but commonly applied to the
hyacinth bean (<spn>Dolichos Lablab</spn>).</def>⟦br⟧
